reviewText: Had the pleasure of seeing this play at the Logan Theater in Chicago. Loved it.

Although the acting was occasionally awkward and the story was pretty weak, still I liked it if for no other reason than the originality of a punk rock musical.

Now, where did I put my spike collar?

This is an awesome movie! If you like punk rock and fantasy stories intertwined into a musical a la Jesus Christ Superstar, you will like this one. And it comes with a digital download of the soundtrack album! Don't let this gem slip you by. Enjoy!
